# UI Component Patterns

## Navigation Structure
[BottomBarView.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/BottomBarView.swift) provides tab navigation:
- Custom tab bar with workout-themed icons
- Active state management
- Dark/light mode support
- Consistent navigation patterns

## Common UI Modifiers
[SwipeActionsAndAlertsModifiers.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/SwipeActionsAndAlertsModifiers.swift) contains reusable modifiers:
- Swipe actions for workout management
- Alert dialogs for confirmations
- Consistent styling across the app
- Animation patterns for user feedback

## Gesture Handling
[SwipeDownToDismissModifier.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/SwipeDownToDismissModifier.swift) provides:
- Swipe-to-dismiss functionality
- Custom gesture recognizers
- Consistent interaction patterns
- Accessibility support

## Workout Display Components
[WorkoutView.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/WorkoutView.swift) and [WorkoutsView.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/WorkoutsView.swift):
- Individual workout cards
- List and grid layouts
- Favourite status indicators
- Completion status display

## Form Components
[AddWorkout.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/AddWorkout.swift) contains complex form elements:
- Custom text fields with scroll behavior
- Location picker with map integration
- Template selection interface
- Validation and error states

## Settings Interface
[SettingsView.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/SettingsView.swift) provides:
- Hierarchical navigation structure
- Form-based settings
- Toggle switches and pickers
- Consistent styling patterns

## Calendar Components
[CalendarView.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/CalendarView.swift) implements:
- Custom calendar interface
- Date selection and navigation
- Workout indicators on dates
- Month/year navigation

## Toolbar Components
[ToolbarView.swift](mdc:WorkoutTracker/ToolbarView.swift) provides:
- Common toolbar actions
- Search functionality
- Filter controls
- Add workout button

## Design System
- Consistent color scheme support
- Dark/light mode adaptation
- Typography hierarchy
- Spacing and layout consistency
- Icon usage patterns
